text: And knowing their sorrow, I am come down to deliver them out of the hands of the Egyptians, and to bring them out of that land into a good and spacious land, into a land that floweth with milk and honey, to the places of the Channonite, and Hethite, and Ammerhite, and Ferezite, and Hevite, and Jebus.
